Over five painstaking years,
Columbia's genetic research facility...

92
00:08:10,907 --> 00:08:15,286
- You gonna talk to her now?
- Oh, no. Come on. You talk to her.

93
00:08:15,495 --> 00:08:17,414
Armed with these DNA blueprints...

94
00:08:17,580 --> 00:08:20,250
...we have now begun
what was once thought impossible.

95
00:08:20,458 --> 00:08:24,129
- Disgusting.
- Yeah, hateful little things.

96
00:08:24,337 --> 00:08:25,714
I love them.

97
00:08:26,256 --> 00:08:27,924
Yeah, me too.

98
00:08:28,883 --> 00:08:32,762
You know, spiders
can change their color...

99
00:08:32,929 --> 00:08:36,766
- ...to blend into their environment.
- Really?

100
