...into these 15 genetically
designed super-spiders.

104
00:08:52,949 --> 00:08:54,451
There's 14.

105
00:08:54,909 --> 00:08:56,286
I beg your pardon?

106
00:08:56,453 --> 00:08:58,538
- One's missing.
