122
00:09:55,637 --> 00:09:56,888
Perfect.

123
00:10:04,646 --> 00:10:06,189
- Is that good?
- Great.

124
00:10:11,736 --> 00:10:12,862
That's great.

125
00:10:18,701 --> 00:10:20,703
M.J., let's go!

126
00:10:22,247 --> 00:10:24,833
Wait. Thanks!

127
00:10:38,304 --> 00:10:41,057
Parker, let's do it.

128
00:10:57,782 --> 00:11:01,244
We solved the horizon glide
and the multi-G balance issues.

129
00:11:01,411 --> 00:11:03,955
I've already seen the glider.

130
00:11:04,372 --> 00:11:06,416
That's not what I'm here for.

131
00:11:06,624 --> 00:11:09,294
General Slocum,
good to see you again.

132
00:11:10,128 --> 00:11:12,297
Mr. Balkan, Mr. Fargas.

133
00:11:12,463 --> 00:11:14,382
- Norman.
- Mr. Osborn.

134
00:11:14,549 --> 00:11:18,094
Always a pleasure to have our
board of directors pay us a little visit.

135
00:11:18,303 --> 00:11:21,723
I want to see the progress report
on human performance enhancers.

136
00:11:21,890 --> 00:11:24,350
We tried vapor inhalation
with rodent subjects.

137
00:11:24,517 --> 00:11:26,352
