204
00:17:03,606 --> 00:17:04,899
Norman!

205
00:17:06,067 --> 00:17:07,109
Norman!

206
00:17:15,618 --> 00:17:16,953
Oh, my God.

207
00:17:18,287 --> 00:17:21,582
Oh, my God! Norman?

208
00:17:22,250 --> 00:17:24,377
Oh, my God! Norman!

209
00:17:26,587 --> 00:17:27,713
Norman.

210
00:17:40,518 --> 00:17:41,978
Back to formula?

211
