Weird.

212
00:18:29,442 --> 00:18:30,818
- Peter?
- Yeah?

213
00:18:31,027 --> 00:18:32,069
Are you all right?

214
00:18:32,236 --> 00:18:33,237
Uh...

215
00:18:34,697 --> 00:18:36,324
I'm fine.

216
00:18:36,866 --> 00:18:38,743
Any better this morning? Any change?

217
00:18:38,909 --> 00:18:40,578
Change?

218
00:18:41,287 --> 00:18:43,205
Yep. Big change.

219
00:18:43,372 --> 00:18:47,460
- Well, hurry up. You'll be late.
